<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Sanction Letter & Key Fact Statement</title>
  <style>
    /* --- KEEPING YOUR EXISTING CSS EXACTLY AS IT IS --- */
    .logos {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      /* puts one left, one right */
      align-items: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .logos img {
      max-width: 170px;
      height: auto;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
    }

    .document-container {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 1000px;
      /* or 1200px */
      margin: 20px auto;
      background: white;
      padding: 40px;
    }

    .document-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .document-header h1 {
      color: #2c3e50;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    .basic-info {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }

    .info-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .info-table td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
    }

    .info-table td:first-child {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .intro-text {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      text-align: justify;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .intro-text p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      color: #555;
    }

    .loan-details h3,
    .loan-parameters h3,
    .contingent-charges h3,
    .other-disclosures h3,
    .repayment-schedule h3,
    .terms-conditions h3 {
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .details-table,
    .parameters-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .details-table td,
    .parameters-table td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .details-table td:first-child,
    .parameters-table td:first-child {
      width: 50px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .details-table td:nth-child(2),
    .parameters-table td:nth-child(2) {
      width: 50%;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .details-table td:last-child,
    .parameters-table td:last-child {
      width: 40%;
    }

    .parameters-table th {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      color: #333333;
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: center;
      font-weight: bold;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }

    .schedule-table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .schedule-table th,
    .schedule-table td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 14px;
      background-color: white;
    }

    .schedule-table th {
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      color: #333333;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .schedule-table tr:nth-child(even) {
      background-color: #f8f9fa;
    }

    .terms-conditions {
      margin-top: 30px;
    }

    .terms-conditions ol {
      margin-left: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .terms-conditions li {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      text-align: justify;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .terms-conditions ul {
      margin-left: 20px;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }

    .terms-conditions ul li {
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .acknowledgement {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding-top: 20px;
    }

    .acknowledgement p {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .signature-area {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: left;
    }

    .signature-area p {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .indent-point {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-left: 18px;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="document-container">
    <div class="logos">
      <img src="<%= backendBaseUrl %>/public/logos/RuleMudra_Prime Logo.png" alt="RuleMudra Logo" class="logo-left" />
      <img src="<%= backendBaseUrl %>/public/logos/Decimus Logo.png" alt="Decimus logo" class="logo-right" />
    </div>
    <header class="document-header">
      <h1>SANCTION LETTER & KEY FACT STATEMENT</h1>
    </header>

    <section class="basic-info">
      <table class="info-table">
        <tr>
          <td>Date</td>
          <td>Name of R.E.</td>
          <td>Applicant Name</td>
          <td>Loan Number</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <% if (approval_detail && approval_detail.createdDate) { %>
              <%=new Date(approval_detail.createdDate).toLocaleDateString('en-GB')%>
                <% } else { %>
                  <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB') %>
                    <%} %>
          </td>
          <td>
            <% if (lender_detail && lender_detail.lender_display_name) { %>
              <%= lender_detail.lender_display_name %>
                <% } else { %> Yashik Finlease Private Limited <% } %>
          </td>
          <td>
            <% if (customer_detail && (customer_detail.customerName || customer_detail.name)) { %>
              <%= customer_detail.customerName || customer_detail.name %>
                <% } else { %> N/A <% } %>
          </td>
          <td>
            <%= (loan_detail && loan_detail.loanNo) ? loan_detail.loanNo : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="intro-text">
      <p>
        <strong>
          M/s. <%= (lender_detail && lender_detail.lender_display_name) ? lender_detail.lender_display_name
            : "Yashik Finlease Private Limited" %>
        </strong>
        ("Lender/ R.E.") is pleased to inform you ("Borrower") that you are
        eligible for a loan facility, subject to the terms and conditions set
        out herein.
      </p>
      <p>
        The Loan is being facilitated through the technology platform of <strong>M/s. Twominutes Fintech Pvt.
          Ltd.</strong> ("Lending Service Provider" or "LSP"), pursuant to an arrangement between <%= (lender_detail &&
          lender_detail.lender_display_name) ? lender_detail.lender_display_name : "Yashik Finlease Private Limited" %>
          and Twominutes Fintech Pvt. Ltd.
      </p>
      <p>
        We are pleased to communicate the <em>in-principal</em> sanction of
        the loan facility, the details of which are set forth below:
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="loan-details">
      <h3>Key Loan Terms</h3>
      <table class="details-table">
        <tr>
          <td>1</td>
          <td>Lender</td>
          <td>
            <%= (lender_detail && lender_detail.lender_display_name) ? lender_detail.lender_display_name
              : "Yashik Finlease Private Limited" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>LSP</td>
          <td>Twominutes Fintech Pvt. Ltd</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>3</td>
          <td>Proposal Validity</td>
          <td>5 days</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>4</td>
          <td>Application ID</td>
          <td>
            <%= (lead_detail && lead_detail.leadID) ? lead_detail.leadID : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td>5</td>
          <td>
            <h3>Applicant Details</h3>
          </td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td>Name</td>
          <td>
            <% if (customer_detail && (customer_detail.customerName || customer_detail.name)) { %>
              <%= customer_detail.customerName || customer_detail.name %>
                <% } else { %> N/A <% } %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td>Address</td>
          <td>
            <% if (address && address.address) { %>
              <%= address.address %>
                <% } else { %> N/A <% } %>
          </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td>PAN</td>
          <td>
            <%= (customer_detail && customer_detail.pancard) ? customer_detail.pancard : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td>Aadhaar</td>
          <td>
            XXXX-XXXX-<%= (customer_detail && customer_detail.aadharNo) ? customer_detail.aadharNo : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td>Date Of Birth</td>
          <td>
            <%= (customer_detail && customer_detail.dob) ? new Date(customer_detail.dob).toLocaleDateString('en-GB')
              : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td>Mobile</td>
          <td>
            <% if (customer_detail && (customer_detail.mobileNo || customer_detail.mobile)) { %>
              <%= customer_detail.mobileNo || customer_detail.mobile %>
                <% } else { %> N/A <% } %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td>Email</td>
          <td>
            <% if (customer_detail && (customer_detail.email || customer_detail.emailId)) { %>
              <%= customer_detail.email || customer_detail.emailId %>
                <% } else { %> N/A <% } %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>6</td>
          <td>Purpose</td>
          <td>
            <%= (lead_detail && lead_detail.purpose) ? lead_detail.purpose : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>7</td>
          <td>
            <h3>Disbursement Through Bank Transfer</h3>
          </td>
          <td></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td>Bank Name</td>
          <td>
            <%= (account_detail && account_detail.bank_name) ? account_detail.bank_name : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td>IFSC Code</td>
          <td>
            <%= (account_detail && account_detail.ifsc) ? account_detail.ifsc : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td></td>
          <td>Account Number</td>
          <td>
            <%= (account_detail && account_detail.account_number) ? account_detail.account_number : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>8</td>
          <td>Tenure (in Days)</td>
          <td>
            <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.tenure) ? approval_detail.tenure : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="loan-parameters">
      <h3>Financial Terms</h3>
      <table class="parameters-table">
        <tr>
          <th>Sr. No.</th>
          <th>Parameters</th>
          <th>Amount (₹)</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>(i)</td>
          <td>Loan Sanctioned</td>
          <td>
            <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.loanAmtApproved) ? approval_detail.loanAmtApproved : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>(ii)</td>
          <td>Total Interest Payable</td>
          <td>
            <%= intem ? Math.round(intem) : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>(iii)</td>
          <td>Processing Fees</td>
          <td>
            <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.adminFee) ? Math.round(approval_detail.adminFee) : "NIL" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>(iv)</td>
          <td>Net Disbursement ((i)-(iii))</td>
          <td>
            <%= fdb ? Math.round(fdb) : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>(v)</td>
          <td>Total Amount Payable by Borrower ((i)+(ii))</td>
          <td>
            <%= rep1 ? Math.round(rep1) : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>(vi)</td>
          <td>Interest Rate Per day (%)</td>
          <td>
            <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.roi) ? approval_detail.roi : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>(vii)</td>
          <td>Annual Percentage Rate (APR)%</td>
          <td>
            <%= apr ? apr.toFixed(2) : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>(viii)</td>
          <td>Tenure (in Days)</td>
          <td>
            <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.tenure) ? approval_detail.tenure : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>(ix)</td>
          <td>No. of Instalments</td>
          <td>1</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>(x)</td>
          <td>Instalment Amount</td>
          <td>
            <%= rep1 ? Math.round(rep1) : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="contingent-charges">
      <h3>Contingent Charges</h3>
      <table class="parameters-table">
        <tr>
          <td>1</td>
          <td>Penal charges for delay in payments of dues</td>
          <td>₹100 per day for the delay</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>NACH/e-Mandate Bounce Charges</td>
          <td>₹500 + GST</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>3</td>
          <td>Statement of Account (SOA) Charges</td>
          <td>Nil</td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="other-disclosures">
      <h3>Other Disclosures</h3>
      <table class="parameters-table">
        <tr>
          <td>1</td>
          <td>Cooling-off / Look-up Period</td>
          <td>3 days</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>2</td>
          <td>
            Details of LSP acting as recovery agent and authorized to approach
            the borrower
          </td>
          <td>Twominutes Fintech Pvt. Ltd</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>3</td>
          <td>
            Name, designation, address and phone number of nodal grievance
            redressal officer designated specifically to deal with FinTech/
            digital lending related complaints/ issues
          </td>
          <td>
            <strong>Name :Mr.Sourav Pandey</strong><br />
            <strong>Designation: Grievance Redressal Officer</strong><br />
            <strong>Address: Hs No 56 Kurmanchal Niketan Apartment I.P Extension Ward Vinod Nagar Shahdara South Zone
              New Delhi – 110092</strong><br />
            <strong>Email : grievance@decimus.co.in</strong>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="repayment-schedule">
      <h3>Repayment Schedule (Tentative)</h3>
      <table class="schedule-table">
        <tr>
          <th>Instalment No.</th>
          <th>Principal (₹)</th>
          <th>Interest (₹)</th>
          <th>Instalment (₹)</th>
          <th>Due Date</th>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>One</td>
          <td>
            <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.loanAmtApproved) ? approval_detail.loanAmtApproved : "N/A" %>
          </td>
          <td>
            <%= intem ? Math.round(intem) : "N/A" %>
          </td>
          <td>
            <%= rep1 ? Math.round(rep1) : "N/A" %>
          </td>
          <td>
            <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.repayDate) ? new
              Date(approval_detail.repayDate).toLocaleDateString('en-GB') : "N/A" %>
          </td>
        </tr>
      </table>
    </section>

    <section class="terms-conditions">
      <h3>General Terms & Conditions</h3>
      <ol>
        <li>
          <p>
            1. This sanction is provisional and issued based on the information,
            declarations, and documents submitted by the Applicant. The Lender
            reserves the absolute right to:
          </p>

          <p class="indent-point">(i) verify such information independently;</p>

          <p class="indent-point">
            (ii) modify, suspend, or cancel the sanction at any stage prior to
            disbursement, without assigning any reason.
          </p>

          <p>
            The Loan shall be disbursed strictly subject to the execution of
            definitive loan documents, successful verification, and compliance with
            the internal credit policies of the Lender.
          </p>

          <p>
            The Lender shall have the right to revoke this sanction if it is not
            accepted within five (5) days from the date of issuance.
          </p>
        </li>
        <li>
          2. The Borrower shall be solely and absolutely liable for repayment of
          the Loan, together with interest, charges, and all applicable dues,
          irrespective of:
          <br /><br />

          <div class="sub-point">
            (i) the purpose for which the Loan is utilized,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (ii) any dispute with third parties,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (iii) any service or facilitation provided by the LSP.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          3. No delay or omission by the Lender or the LSP in exercising any right or remedy shall operate as a waiver
          thereof,
          nor shall any single or partial exercise preclude any further exercise of such rights.
        </li>
        <li>
          4. Upon the occurrence of any default, including non-payment,
          misrepresentation, or breach of terms, the Lender shall have the
          absolute right to:
          <br /><br />

          <div class="sub-point">
            (i) recall the entire Loan amount with immediate effect,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (ii) levy penal charges,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (iii) initiate recovery proceedings as permissible under law.
          </div>

          <br />

          The Borrower shall not be entitled to any prior notice in such cases.
        </li>
        <li>
          5. The Borrower expressly consents to the Lender and the LSP collecting,
          storing, processing, and sharing data with:
          <br /><br />

          <div class="sub-point">
            (i) Credit Information Companies,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (ii) Regulatory authorities, including the Reserve Bank of India,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (iii) Service providers engaged for loan facilitation.
          </div>

          <br />

          The LSP shall act only as a data processor/facilitator and shall not
          be responsible for decisions taken by the Lender based on such data.
        </li>
        <li>
          6. The Lender may undertake recovery actions directly or through authorized representatives in accordance with
          applicable laws.The LSP may assist in communication strictly as a facilitation service and shall not be deemed
          a
          recovery agent unless separately authorized.
        </li>
        <li>
          7. The Borrower agrees to indemnify and keep indemnified the Lender and
          the LSP, including their officers and affiliates, against any losses,
          claims, damages, or liabilities arising from:
          <br /><br />

          <div class="sub-point">
            (i) breach of terms,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (ii) misuse of loan funds,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (iii) incorrect information provided by the Borrower,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (iv) any third-party claims arising out of the Borrower’s actions.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          8. The Borrower confirms that:
          <br /><br />

          <div class="sub-point">
            (i) all terms have been read and understood,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (ii) the Loan is availed at their sole discretion,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (iii) no reliance has been placed on any representation other than
            those contained herein.
          </div>
        </li>

        <li>
          9. The Borrower shall utilize the Loan strictly for the purpose stated in
          the application. The Lender reserves the right to verify end-use at
          any time.
          <br /><br />

          Any diversion or misuse of funds shall constitute an event of default,
          entitling the Lender to recall the entire Loan immediately.
        </li>

        <li>
          10. The Lender shall have the right of set-off and lien against any
          monies, deposits, or balances of the Borrower available with the
          Lender, whether singly or jointly held, towards adjustment of any
          outstanding dues under this Loan.
        </li>

        <li>
          11. The Borrower agrees to indemnify and hold harmless the Lender and the
          LSP, including their respective directors, employees, agents, and
          affiliates, from and against any losses, claims, damages, liabilities,
          costs, or expenses arising out of:
          <br /><br />

          <div class="sub-point">
            (i) breach of terms by the Borrower,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (ii) misuse or diversion of loan funds,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (iii) incorrect or misleading information,
          </div>

          <div class="sub-point">
            (iv) any third-party claims attributable to the Borrower.
          </div>
        </li>

        <li>
          APR has been computed as the effective annualized interest rate on the
          net disbursed amount, using the IRR (Internal Rate of Return)
          approach.
        </li>

        <li>
          Within the Cooling-off Period, the Borrower may prepay the loan
          principal without incurring any prepayment penalty. Post this period,
          prepayment charges shall apply.
        </li>

        <li>
          In the event of default, the Lender and/or the Reserve Bank of India
          (RBI) and/or Credit Information Companies (CICs) may publish the
          Borrower's name as a defaulter, at their sole discretion.
        </li>

        <li>
          The Borrower hereby consents to the Lender disclosing and sharing
          their personal and financial information with RBI, CICs, professional
          advisors, affiliates, service providers, and any other agency
          authorized under applicable law.
        </li>

        <br>
        <br>
        <li>
          <strong>For more information, please visit the link below:</strong>
        </li>        
        <li>
          <a href="https://rulemudra.com/privacy-policy.html">https://rulemudra.com/privacy-policy.html</a>
        </li>
      </ol>
    </section>

    <section class="acknowledgement">
      <br />
      <h3><strong>Acknowledgement</strong></h3>
      <p>
        <% if (customer_detail && (customer_detail.customerName || customer_detail.name)) { %> I, <%=
            customer_detail.customerName || customer_detail.name %>, hereby acknowledge that I have read, understood,
            and accepted the terms and conditions specified herein and in the Loan Proposal. <% } else { %> I, (Name of
              borrower), hereby acknowledge that I have read, understood, and accepted the terms and conditions
              specified herein and in the Loan Proposal. <% } %>
      </p>
      <div class="signature-area">
        <p>
          Acknowledgement Date: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB') %>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</body>

</html>